# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.
#
# This .gitignore file comprehensively covers:
# - Dependencies (node_modules, package manager files)
# - Build outputs (.next, dist, build)
# - Environment variables and sensitive files (.env.*)
# - API keys, credentials, and security files
# - Cache and temporary files
# - IDE and OS-specific files
# - Media files (videos, audio)
# - Documentation files (*.md except README.md)
# - Project-specific outputs (captions, rendered videos)

